  <prompt>
After T140-T144 land their fixes, operator runs end-to-end UAT against spaarkedev1 for all 5 wizards: file summary, document create profile, Create Matter, Create Project, Create Work Assignment. Verifies wave12 plan ACs §3.2 (AC8-AC12).
  </prompt>

  <role>
You facilitate operator UAT; document outcomes; capture defects as ISS-NNN if any surface.
  </role>

  <goal>
All 5 wizards confirmed working end-to-end by operator. All AC8-AC12 (wave12 plan §3.2) signed off.
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    - T140: wizard file summary fix applied
    - T141: document create profile fix applied
    - T142: Project wizard FK re-linked
    - T143: Matter wizard verified
    - T144: WA wizard verified
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    - Operator-driven; out-of-band activity
    - Defects captured via /project-defer-issue-tracking → ISS-NNN
    - Critical defects gate Wave 12.5 wrap-up
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      - projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r7/notes/wave12-mvp-completion-plan.md (§3.2 ACs)
      - projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r7/notes/audits/wave12-12{1,2,3}-*.md (audit resolutions)
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <relevant-files>
      - All wizard UI components (5 wizards)
      - All wizard BFF endpoints
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <steps>
1. **Request operator UAT** (operator-time):
   - Provide checklist of 5 wizards × representative test scenario each
   - Operator runs each in browser against spaarkedev1
2. **Capture outcomes** per wizard (15 min each):
   - ✅ Pass (signoff)
   - ⚠️ Minor issues (capture as ISS-NNN)
   - ❌ Critical fail (escalate; do NOT proceed to Wave 12.5)
3. **Update audit notes + wrap-up doc** (30 min):
   - Notes/handoffs/wave12-3-uat-signoff.md with per-wizard outcomes
   - Append final state to each audit's Resolution subsection

  </steps>

  <tools>
    - Bash (operator scheduling; doc updates)
    - mcp__claude_ai_Claude_Code_Remote__create_trigger (optional — schedule UAT reminder)
    - TodoWrite
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    - notes/handoffs/wave12-3-uat-signoff.md
